Source: univention-session
Section: univention
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Univention GmbH <packages@univention.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper, univention-config-dev, libunivention-config-dev, libunivention-debug-dev, ucslint
Standards-Version: 3.8.2

Package: univention-session-server
Architecture: any
Replaces: univention-client-login
Conflicts: univention-client-login
Depends: ${shlib:Depends}, univention-skel
Description: UCS - session manager (server part)
 Univention Session manages desktop sessions. It keeps
 track of processes started and terminates them when the
 session is over. Server and client exchange alive messages
 so that it can quickly be detect when either one becomes
 unavailable.
 .
 This package provides the server part.

Package: univention-session-client
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlib:Depends}, rsh-client
Description: UCS - session manager (client part)
 Univention Session manages desktop sessions. It keeps
 track of processes started and terminates them when the
 session is over. Server and client exchange alive messages
 so that it can quickly be detect when either one becomes
 unavailable.
 .
 This package provides the client part.
